    <item>
      <title>衰退贸易吞噬了关税战的华尔街</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在金融市场的每个角落，从股票到债券再到商品，货币经理都向唐纳德·特朗普发送了同样的信息：他释放的贸易战争威胁要引发全球衰退＆Mdash＆Mdash;和快速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:27:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔信号仍被搁置，警惕持续的价格冲击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/powell-signals-fed-would-respond-to-persistent-inflation-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）表示，新关税的经济影响可能会大大比预期的要大得多，并且中央银行必须确保这不会导致通货膨胀越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/powell-signals-fed-would-respond-to-persistent-inflation-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Newsom说，加利福尼亚寻求盟友的关税豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）表示，他正在寻求对加利福尼亚制造产品的报复性关税的豁免，并希望与全球盟友就新的贸易关系进行谈判，这使该州成为反对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的大量关税计划的后果的缓冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
