    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战的掩盖鲍威尔和乔布斯，美国国债集会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/treasuries-hold-4-line-as-jobs-report-powell-speech-loom-large</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国债攀升了，交易员提高了他们对美联储削减利益降低的赌注，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税的后果使市场又消除了一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/treasuries-hold-4-line-as-jobs-report-powell-speech-loom-large</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股票下沉，因为鲍威尔（Powell）表示急于降低税率：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票的抛售加深了，债券削减了收益和石油的销量为四年低点，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）重申了中央银行的等待方式，尽管表明贸易战的经济损失将比预期的要大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
